  • Method Details

    • exec

      public String[] exec(Command cmd)
      Executes cmd. Returns list of commands to execute later. It's required for execution not to happen outside of interpreter (otherwise some commands have to run other commands inside themselves).
      Parameters:
      cmd - command for interpretation
      Returns:
      list of commands for later interpretation or null
